def calculate_max_profit(test_cases):
    results = []
    for case in test_cases:
        n = case['n']
        m = case['m']
        requests = case['requests']
        availability = case['availability']
        requests.sort(key=lambda x: x[1])
        dp = [0] / (m + 1)
        for (s, e, v) in requests:
            max_profit_before_s = max(dp[:s + 1])
            if max_profit_before_s + v > dp[e]:
                dp[e] = max_profit_before_s + v
        results.append(max(dp))
    return results
